quran[46]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,"M wẽen ne malεgs nins sẽn võogd kɩfr-dãmbã yõyã pãng-pãngã."
  79,2,"La ne [malεgs nins] sẽn reegd sɩd-kõtbã yõyã yol-yolã."
  79,3,"La ne sigdbã tɩ b yaa sẽn laande."
  79,4,"La ne põsdbã sẽn rengd taab n na mɑɑn Wẽnd sɑglgã."
  79,5,"La ne mɑlεgs nins sẽn yikd ne Wẽnd sɑglsã m mɑɑnd-ɑ wã."
  79,6,"Raar ning rĩmsgã sẽn na n rĩmsã (Baorgã fʋʋs raẽengã)."
  79,7,"Tɩ fʋʋsg a yiibẽ soabã pʋgl-a."
  79,8,"Baraare sũy n rigimdidi."
  79,9,"B ninã yaa sẽn nodge."
  79,10,"B yetame: ""rẽ yĩnga b na n lebs-d-la yiibã zĩigẽ (dũni)."""
  79,11,"Tɩ tõnd sã n wa lebg kõab sẽn weele."
  79,12,"B yetame: ""rẽnda yaa bõn lebgre""."
  79,13,"La ad yẽnda yaa tãs-vuk bala."
  79,14,"Tɩ bãmb yaa sẽn be vʋʋgr n be rasempʋɩɩgẽ wã."
  79,15,"Rẽ yĩngã a Musa kibarã waa fo nengẽ?"
  79,16,"Wakat ning a Soabã sẽn wa n boaal-a Ṭuuwaa koso-yɩlengẽ wã."
  79,17,"Kẽng a Fɩr-ʿaoon nengẽ, bala a kedgame."
  79,18,"N tɩ yεεl-a ""rẽ yĩnga f na sak n yɩlg f menga?"""
  79,19,"Tɩ m peeg-f n tʋg f Soabẽ wã tɩ f yaees-A ."
  79,20,"T'a wilg-a yel-soalem bεdã."
  79,21,"T'a yags la a kɩɩse."
  79,22,"Rẽ poorẽ, a gõda a kuidg n fãeesdẽ."
  79,23,"N tʋg n tigim ɑ tãpã n moone."
  79,24,"N yeele: ""Maam la yãmb soaben-zẽkdgã""."
  79,25,"Tɩ Wẽnd wẽbg-a ne Yaoolem la Dũni naongã."
  79,26,"Ad bãng-yam be rẽnda pʋgẽ ne ned ning sẽn yaeesda."
  79,27,"Rẽ yĩnga yãmb naaneg n yɩɩd keelem bɩ yaa saagã? Wẽnd sẽn me-a wã."
  79,28,"A zẽka a beoongã n zems a taaba."
  79,29,"N sobg a yʋngã la A vẽneg a wĩndgã."
  79,30,"La Tẽngã, rẽ poorẽ lɑ A yɑdg-a."
  79,31,"A yiisa a pʋgẽ a koomã la a yamdã."
  79,32,"La tãmsã, A sεl-b lame."
  79,33,"Yaa wʋm-noog ne yãmb la y rũmsã."
  79,34,"La yel-bed-kεgengã sã n wa( bɑrgã fʋʋs yɩlengã)."
  79,35,"Raar ning ninsaal sẽn na n tagsd bũmb ning a sẽn tʋmã."
  79,36,"Tɩ b vẽneg Gεhɩɩm ne net fãa."
  79,37,"La ned ning sẽn maan-a n zʋʋge."
  79,38,"La a yɩɩs Dũni vɩɩmã."
  79,39,"Bɩ f bãng tɩ yaa Gεhɩɩm la a gãag zĩiga."
  79,40,"La sã n yaa ned ning sẽn yaees a Soabã ziiri, la a gɩdg yõorã n yi ɑ yamleoogo."
  79,41,"Bɩ f bãng tɩ Arzãn la a gãag zĩiga."
  79,42,"B sokda foo dũni yikr yelle, a yɩɩbã yaa rabʋre?"
  79,43,"Bõe la fo mi a pʋgẽ n nɑ n togse?"
  79,44,"A bãngrã gill bee ne fo Soabã."
  79,45,"Ad fo yaa bugsd ne ned ning sẽn yaeesd-a."
  79,46,"Raar ning b sẽn na n ya wala bãmb pa zĩnd dũni sã n pa zaabr bala, ma yibeoogo."
